name: Fly Guy District, Inc. (Trademark Tee) Organic Blue
description:
Fly Guy District's Offical Trademark Tee

- 100% Sheer Jersey cotton construction  
- Durable rib neckband 
- Unisex style.
- Fabric weight 3.8 oz/yd² (129 g/m²)

Pre-shrunk and laundered, our 100% cotton Sheer Jersey is combed for softness and comfort. Comprised of loosely knit 40-singles yarn, this fabric has both a subtle stretch and delicate texture. 

Shipping: USPS Priority Mail to US and International Destinations.
Usually Ships within 1 to 2 days.
